text: Daxing Subdistrict () is a subdistrict in Songtao Miao Autonomous County, Guizhou, China. , it has 3 residential communities and 7 villages under its administration. == See also == * List of township-level divisions of Guizhou == References == Category:Township-level divisions of Guizhou Category:Songtao Miao Autonomous County
